UNITED STATES of America v. Curtis ABBEY et al. No. 7394. United States Court of Appeals Tenth Circuit. Aug. 8, 1963. Newell A. George, U. S. Atty., and Ronald K. Badger, Asst. U. S. Atty., Topeka, Kan., for appellant. L. R. Hannen, Burlington, Kan., for appellees.

Before MURRAH, Chief Judge, and BREITENSTEIN, Circuit Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed August 8, 1963, on joint motion of the parties.
